Catwoman actress Michelle Pfeiffer, 64, showed age is just a number as she posted snaps from her July 4th celebrations. Without a stitch of make-up, Michelle graced her followers with her stunning ageless complexion. She captioned the photo in view of her 2.3 million Instagram followers: "No better way to have spent the 4th of July than with my two beautiful and brilliant sisters. "Lucky, lucky me. Hope you all had a nice day too." Social media users rushed to the comments to compliment the Hollywood star on her youthful appearance. Timstachula0729 said: "Wow, a beautiful angel inside and out." Bjohnson.yachts added: "You look great. Stay natural."